testtool.models.student

Class TakeTest

  • java.lang.Object
    • testtool.models.student.TakeTest

  • public class TakeTest
extends java.lang.Object
    Author:
    Alvin TakeTest is the test the student is currently taking. TimeRemaining is the time before the test is closed. The List AnsweredQuestions keeps track of which questions were answered. currentQuestion is the currently selected question. StudentAnswers is the list of all answers the student submits as well as the student's information and test for which the answers are for
